version 2.1402
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
.Vb 1
\&    use Moose::Deprecated \-api_version => $version;
.Ve
.SH "FUNCTIONS"
.IX Header "FUNCTIONS"
This module manages deprecation warnings for features that have been
deprecated in Moose.
.PP
If you specify \f(CW\*(C`\-api_version => $version\*(C'\fR, you can use deprecated features
without warnings. Note that this special treatment is limited to the package
that loads \f(CW\*(C`Moose::Deprecated\*(C'\fR.
